Package: alphaopics
Type: Package
Title: Species-Specific Light Exposure Calculator
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2025-11-24
Authors@R:
    person("Altug", "Didikoglu",
           email = "altug.didikoglu@manchester.ac.uk",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5582-6956"))
Description: Provides tools to calculate species-specific a-opic light exposure metrics 
    for ecological and photobiological research. The package includes datasets for 
    species-specific photopigment sensitivities and prereceptoral filtering. Functions 
    calculate Govardovskii visual pigment templates and return results in terms of 
    a-opic radiance/irradiance, photon radiance/irradiance, and equivalent 
    daylight illuminance/luminance. Additional tools compute photopic illuminance 
    and biological light detection indices to support light pollution assessments.
